snippet.title: Battle Axe - Druid Gameplay Preview
snippet.description:
Heading into the final 24 hours of Kickstarter: https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/henknieborg/battle-axe

Despite his years, the Druid is more than capable of taking care of himself hurling fireballs at his foes whilst flitting around the battlefield with his teleport ability.

Find out more: http://numskullgames.com/project/battle-axe/
